Subject: Re: TeleUse, UIM/X, and C++
Message-ID: <199304060629.AA00339@parsival.delft.sgp.slb.com>
Date: 6 Apr 93 02:55:45 GMT
Article-I.D.: parsival.199304060629.AA00339
Sender: news@athena.mit.edu
Organization: The Internet
