Subject: TkMan for Ultrix
Followup-To: comp.lang.tcl
Date: 16 Apr 1993 05:42:06 GMT
Organization: University of California, Berkeley
Lines: 42
Distribution: world
Message-ID: <1qlgve$gfq@agate.berkeley.edu>
