Subject: Re: DESQview/X on a PC?
Organization: Quarterdeck Office Systems, Santa Monica CA
Date: Mon, 19 Apr 1993 17:26:42 GMT
Message-ID: <1993Apr19.172642.1369@qdeck.com>
