Subject: Re: High order bit of a character in xterm .
Date: 21 Apr 1993 14:26:14 -0400
Organization: The Internet
Lines: 33
Sender: news@athena.mit.edu
Message-ID: <9304211336.AA02196@hpfrcu03.france.hp.com>
