Subject: Detecting read-only colorcells?
Message-ID: <1993Apr22.060053.29463@slate.mines.colorado.edu>
Date: 22 Apr 93 06:00:53 GMT
Reply-To: ngorelic@speclab.cr.usgs.gov
Organization: Colorado School of Mines
