Date: 24 Apr 1993 03:55:28 +0200
Lines: 26
Message-ID: <1ra6mg$pbp@rainbow.in-berlin.de>
References: <MAILQUEUE-101.930420145015.384@oak.shu.ac.uk> <1r1q5g$cv4@genesis.ait.psu.edu>
NNTP-Posting-Host: rainbow.in-berlin.de
